-FAQ">Quân minh thần lương - 君明臣良</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/S%E1%BB%9F-Khanh-ho%E1%BA%A1-Ki%E1%BB%81u-t%E1%BA%A1i-Ng%C6%B0ng-B%C3%ADch-l%C3%A2u-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-c%E1%BA%A3m-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-thi/poem-QTKCDgRinybg6F5dLA27cw">Sở Khanh hoạ Kiều tại Ngưng Bích lâu tức cảnh cảm đề thi - 楚卿和翹在凝碧樓即景感題詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%B1-tuy%E1%BB%81n-nh%C3%A3n/poem-B7dXQ8NRFbQt_ao1vjjs6A">Thái Bình tự tuyền nhãn - 太平寺泉眼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-trung/poem-7Udq9h6fJXm538udi9mZdg">Tương trung - 湘中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
